{"tid":2062632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街站宣傳罷課 三學生被捕","createTime":"2020-06-13T09:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:27:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"399eee89e5b1310c8f41c4ab85c5e98668a7f2f5","tid":2062632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/ZJS2EMAHQGBXD4T37CSRDFV45U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FZJS2EMAHQGBXD4T37CSRDFV45U%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f9b858ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FZJS2EMAHQGBXD4T37CSRDFV45U%2F&h=db42c922\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/ZJS2EMAHQGBXD4T37CSRDFV45U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n街站宣傳罷課 三學生被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AA7Z7QQQ2GV4IPJWJ7BQUA5OKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAA7Z7QQQ2GV4IPJWJ7BQUA5OKI.jpg&h=8caf7d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方搶走及扯爛宣傳罷課公投的中學生行動籌備平台街站物資，並拘捕三人。李家皓攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】暴政以限聚。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：旺角大截查  面對惡法 學生：迷惘但企硬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警曾稱不會針對街站<br />\n<br />\n昨晚近9時，銅鑼灣東角道警員突然舉起藍旗，驅逐現正宣傳罷課公投的中學生行動籌備平台街站，隨後更前後包抄衝入金百利商場，搶走及扯毀街站成員手上的物資，包括街站旗幟，並壓倒包括中學生在內的數名在場人士，中學生行動籌備平台三名成員被捕。<br />\n<br />\n鄭家朗指出，警方警民關係科昨向他表示不會針對街站拘捕，<span style=\"color: orange;\">街站運作亦非常和平，成員沒有嗌口號和唱《榮光》，僅展示罷課照片宣傳，亦與其他人距離達三至四米，昨晚收拾物資準備離開時，卻遭警方無理拘捕三名成員，不知加以甚麼罪名</span>。<br />\n<br />\n鄭稱現場區議員聽見警方行動前指着街站說「就係呢班人」，證明警方針對街站有備而來，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍、譚名傑、袁楚雙"},{"pid":"97b024860741a415c28f1052c71394f7d2b79e82","tid":2062632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe93319dc54164af3a4da3c7bcbfa18881f4002","tid":2062632,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"所以直播果陣班狗成日好重覆咁講要驅散暴徒<br />\n<br />\n但係所有cam都睇唔到佢地講緊既野"}]}